{"tid":1849944,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"跪求賣口罩黃店要篩走藍絲","createTime":"2020-01-29T09:58:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T05:56:58.000Z","uid":127972,"like":70,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"8e63d662808094d71092a178fa8cea18ca8062a7","tid":1849944,"uid":127972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:58:07.000Z","msg":"首先感謝為香港人張羅口罩的黃店<br />\n<br />\n程班長阿布泰一送一賣兩件事話俾大家知，好多人好撚自私<br />\n<br />\n（以下純粹建議）<br />\n要杜絕自撚絲，一定唔可以半賣半送口，講明捐俾手足或開宗明義口罩收益撐抗爭，要買就買，唔買的藍絲廢老就走<br />\n<br />\n要篩走藍絲，叫佢地支持返藍色藥房食炒價<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依家大家都需要口罩，賣貴啲可以make noise鞏固黃色經濟圈，又可以留錢俾有需要的地方，係一石二鳥"},{"pid":"20f03269d35ff07cca1a04a39007314b53f2a4de","tid":1849944,"uid":127972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:05:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fb23f7754234b07b2d865e01a4f43bbaf1a97e72","tid":1849944,"uid":69754,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:07:46.000Z","msg":"嗌口號先俾買"},{"pid":"5a444a05c299cdaf8c484d92b2f9f01cde8fa27a","tid":1849944,"uid":275524,"like":2,"dislike":21,"score":-19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:08:27.000Z","msg":"講句口号就有得買"},{"pid":"39d1b0db2ce7a922ecbb8500fb0e34659fdbbcd9","tid":1849944,"uid":249160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:09:48.000Z","msg":"推推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80cebf2d975bd9971e3e5b23a80f0fd4b0ef1952","tid":1849944,"uid":274432,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"5a444a05c299cdaf8c484d92b2f9f01cde8fa27a","tid":1849944,"uid":275524,"like":2,"dislike":21,"score":-19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:08:27.000Z","msg":"講句口号就有得買"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:11:19.000Z","msg":"寫撚番好d字喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/l